com.betfair.cougar.netutil.nio.marshalling

Class ArgumentMatcher

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.betfair.cougar.netutil.nio.marshalling.ArgumentMatcher

  • public class ArgumentMatcher
extends Object
    receives parameter names and parameter values from a client and matches them to the expected parameters of the server.
  • parameter supplied by the client that are not expected by the server are ignored
  • optional parameters expected by the server but not supplied by the client will have a value of null
  • mandatory parameters expected by the server by not supplied by the client will generate an error
